    "title": "Intro to Loops",
    "long_instructions": "**What would be a more descriptive name for `mystery_function`? Explain your answer.**\r\n\r\nMake sure to include an explanation of what the `while` loop is doing.\r\n\r\n```\r\nfrom neighborhood import Painter\r\n\r\nsusana = Painter()\r\n\r\n# Define mystery_function\r\ndef mystery_function:\r\n  while susana.has_paint():\r\n    susana.paint(\"white\")\r\n    susana.move()\r\n\r\n# Run your code\r\nwhile susana.is_on_bucket():\r\n     susana.take_paint()\r\nmystery_function()\r\n``` ",
